node.text: I always had trouble memorizing techniques when I was a beginer in jiu-jitsu so I had no choice but to gravitate towards the principles. Proud of my brothers @renergracie and @ryrongracie for putting together a course that lets anyone learn the 32 principles so efficiently. The course comes out this Saturday and they are having a free live "unveiling" event at 3pm pst if you wanna learn the principles, register at The32Principles.com
